title: Google\Cloud\Optimization\V1\InjectedSolutionConstraint\ConstraintRelaxation\Relaxation\Level
name: Level
description:
Expresses the different constraint relaxation levels, which are applied for a visit and those that follow when it satifies the threshold conditions.

The enumeration below is in order of increasing relaxation.

Protobuf type google.cloud.optimization.v1.InjectedSolutionConstraint.ConstraintRelaxation.Relaxation.Level
